WEBVTT

00:08.341 --> 00:12.471
I wish I could see your sister's face
when she finds Courtney's frog in her bed.

00:12.545 --> 00:15.378
You and me both. This is gonna be good.

00:15.448 --> 00:19.282
If she doesn't scream soon,
I'm gonna have to give my frog a drink.

00:19.352 --> 00:21.252
Ferdinand gets dehydrated.

00:22.956 --> 00:25.015
It's Will and Hilary. Open up.

00:27.327 --> 00:29.921
No. We're all gonna die.

00:32.499 --> 00:34.296
We wanted to say good night.

00:34.367 --> 00:37.894
We're going to bed just as soon
as we finish this frog-leg soup.

00:38.905 --> 00:40.463
Frog-leg soup?

00:40.707 --> 00:44.006
- It's mm-mm good.
- I wish you could have some...

00:44.077 --> 00:47.308
but there wasn't enough frog
to make more than two bowls.

00:47.380 --> 00:51.043
- Can I have a bite?
- Sasha, they're eating Ferdinand.

00:51.518 --> 00:55.284
Ferdinand? This is a guy frog?

00:57.891 --> 01:00.359
Nighty-night. Don't let the snails bite.

01:00.927 --> 01:01.951
Snails?

01:02.128 --> 01:05.928
That's funny, I thought she said
she put snakes in your sleeping bags.

01:06.866 --> 01:08.663
Psych!

01:09.869 --> 01:13.305
- That means "just kidding."
- Nighty-night.

01:13.940 --> 01:15.134
Will?

01:15.308 --> 01:18.539
Will you tell us a scary story
before you go, please?

01:18.678 --> 01:21.806
Okay, but I hope everybody's ready
to be scared to death.

01:21.881 --> 01:23.143
Yes!

01:26.586 --> 01:28.884
Wait. Hold up. Scream for me one time.

01:31.524 --> 01:33.151
That's good.

01:34.894 --> 01:37.658
I got a scary story,
but I have to warn you...

01:38.431 --> 01:41.093
it's really, truly frightening.

01:42.735 --> 01:45.363
- Any of you have pacemakers on?
- No.

01:46.072 --> 01:50.099
See, what makes this story so scary
is that it's true.

01:50.443 --> 01:53.105
It happened to a guy named Will... bert.

01:54.013 --> 01:56.641
Wilbert Smith... sonian.

01:56.883 --> 01:59.613
See, Wilbert Smithsonian
grew up in Philly.

01:59.686 --> 02:01.916
He went to school in the 'hood, right?

02:01.988 --> 02:04.513
But this school he went to was so tough...

02:04.591 --> 02:08.584
I mean, it was graffiti everywhere,
even on the principal.

02:12.031 --> 02:14.192
But that's not the scary part.

02:16.069 --> 02:18.799
It all happened right here in Bel-Air...

02:19.272 --> 02:22.264
when Wilbert was transferred
to a private school.

02:22.675 --> 02:25.235
It was a living nightmare.

